# Local dev secrets for `npx wrangler pages dev dist`. Copy this file to .dev.vars
# (gitignored) and fill in real values. Use the TEST/preview Resend key so local
# sign-ups never touch the production audience. The non-secret vars (RESEND_FROM,
# RESEND_AUDIENCE_VERIFIED_ID, RESEND_CONFIRM_TEMPLATE_ALIAS) come from wrangler.toml —
# only secrets belong here.

# Resend API key (Bearer token).
RESEND_API_KEY="re_..."

# Long random string that signs/verifies the double opt-in confirm token.
RESEND_VERIFY_SECRET="any-long-random-string"
